node.text:
Spring cleaning is in full effect over here and the first thing I did was “strip”my white discolored bedding. I have heard about laundry stripping but I was honestly was a bit skeptical so I had to give it a try for myself!!
.
The results completely shocked me and now nothing in our home is safe from “laundry stripping”. It’s my new obsession!!
.
Click here for direct links to everything I used to make my white sheets new again! 
http://liketk.it/3cj3E
.
.
.

node.text:
Finishing our basement has been so fun and watching each space come together is so rewarding!! This room is a mini suite with an attached bathroom. I love how it turned out! The warm neutral and earthy tones and textures give it a welcoming vibe! Best decisions made was to install wall to wall 100% waterproof vinyl flooring from @officialselectsurfaces it’s gorgeous and locks together perfectly!
.
Check out my video and see this room come to life in under 2 mins!
.
#roomrenovation #building #woodworking #diyprojects #bedroomvibes #homedecor #interiordesign #interiordesigner #cozyvibes #bedroomdesign
